Keep them submerged
as long as you can.

41:42.800 --> 41:44.961
I know how to treat
sore knuckles.

41:45.000 --> 41:47.025
This needs more flour.
You just like

41:47.070 --> 41:48.765
the parallel.

41:48.800 --> 41:50.097
Primitive _a_fterca re
for a primitive sport.

41:50.140 --> 41:53.906
While this might look primitive,

41:53.940 --> 41:57.103
I assure, this is the result

41:57.140 --> 41:58.903
of years
of painstaking research.

41:58.950 --> 42:00.941
It's a poultice
of comfrey leaves and flour

42:00.980 --> 42:03.744
with a dash of mountain arnica
and a sprinkling of marigold.

42:03.780 --> 42:05.213
I highly recommend it.

42:05.250 --> 42:06.979
Unless, of course,
you want your eye

42:07.020 --> 42:08.715
to blacken as a badge of honor.

42:08.760 --> 42:11.081
I just want to put
this whole thing behind me.

42:11.120 --> 42:13.179
